OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain or drizzle through
OL,7,Fthe evening. These easing after
OL,8,Fmidnight to become largely dry by
OL,9,Fdawn. Perhaps some clear spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FDry, but often cloudy
OL,13,Fmorning, with a few brighter or sunny
OL,14,Fspells. Cloud clearing in the
OL,15,Fafternoon to give longer sunny
OL,16,Fperiods. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
