OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,6,FWednesday, and very mild with brighter
OL,7,Fspells, but cloudier to the northwest.
OL,8,FBreezy with rain or showers Thursday.
OL,9,FLikely wet and windy at first Friday,
OL,10,Fthen cooler with showers.
